<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><u>NCS Associate Mentor wave confirmations</u></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">Hey&nbsp;<font face="arial">{!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="arial">We have now confirmed the allocation of NCS Associate Mentors to waves this summer. You can find which wave(s) you have been allocated to by clicking <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1tzV9k8P1e52lVI4Kd9Oti3a3j-j_cpi6w1v7mavZi5U/edit?usp=sharing" style="font-weight: bold;">HERE</a>.</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Please note the following points:</font></b></div><div style="text-align: left;"><ul><li><font face="arial">Applicants have been allocated to a maximum of <b>TWO</b> NCS waves. This means that you may not have been allocated to all of the waves you signed up for.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you <b>cannot find your name</b> anywhere on the sheet, but you have previously filled it in, please reply to this email with your name and desired wave(s).</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you<b> can no longer attend</b> the wave you have been allocated to, please reply to this email to let us know.</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Seven days</b>&nbsp;before your start date on your wave, you will receive an email with further information about locations, times and contacts.</font></li><li><font face="arial">After that, you will <b>receive a call</b> from your Assistant Programme Manager who will answer any questions you have ahead of your placement.</font></li></ul><div><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b>Remember, if you're going to be 18 before the end of August:</b></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><ul><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">You will need to have a Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) check. These can take several weeks to process so if you haven't started the application yet, <b><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionsAMs.pdf">click here and get going</a>!</b></font></li><li><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you have already started your&nbsp;</span>application<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;but not yet completed it, make&nbsp;sure you finish it as soon as possible!</span></font></li><li>If you already completed your application, <b>well done!</b></li><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Once you have&nbsp;received&nbsp;your DBS certificate, you will need to scan it and email it to samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org. You will then need to bring the original copy to your first day on the programme.</b></font></li></ul><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">See you soon!&nbsp;</span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>The Challenge Society</b></div>]]></td>
</tr>
